Recommends: legendary
Description: Gaming performance management and library integration
 GamePerf Manager is a comprehensive gaming performance management
 tool for Linux. It provides integration with Steam, Epic Games Store
 (via Legendary CLI), and Wine/Proton, along with real-time
 performance monitoring and hardware control.
 .
 Features include:
  * Steam library integration
  * Epic Games Store support via Legendary CLI
  * Wine/Proton prefix management
  * Real-time performance monitoring daemon
  * Hardware control with appropriate permissions
